pcsc-lite: PC/SC Lite (Smart cards middleware for the PC/SC standard)
pcsc-lite:
pcsc-lite: PC/SC Lite is a middleware to access a smart card using PC/SC
pcsc-lite: standard (library and daemon). The purpose of PC/SC Lite is to
pcsc-lite: provide a Windows(R) SCard interface in a very small form factor
pcsc-lite: for communicating to smartcards and readers.
pcsc-lite: The PC/SC daemon is used to dynamically allocate/deallocate
pcsc-lite: reader drivers at runtime and manage connections to the readers.
pcsc-lite: The PC/SC Lite library is used to connect to the PC/SC daemon
pcsc-lite: from a client application and provide access to the desired
pcsc-lite: reader.
pcsc-lite: Packaged by Georgi D. Sotirov <gdsotirov@dir.bg>
